author: PlayStation
description:
Traveller, harness the power of PlayStation®5 consoles for the ultimate open-world RPG experience in a vast magical realm of adventure.

Feel Teyvat come to life with lightning-fast load times, mesmerizing 4K visuals1, and immersive haptic feedback.

Claim your bonus Geode of Replication crystals and let your imagination run wild in the upcoming Miliastra Wonderland mode.

Redemption codes will be distributed via email. Genshin Impact players who have played via their account for PlayStation® in the past three months will receive the redemption code to their connected email address. Excludes mainland China. 

The offer is valid from 3pm PDT on October 21 2025, until 1:59am PST on December 2 2025.

Travellers can visit the Redeem Code page on the official Genshin Impact website to complete the redemption: genshin.hoyoverse.com/en/gift. 

Travellers playing on PlayStation®5 consoles should ensure that the HoYoverse account linked to their account for PlayStation® has a verified email ad
title: Genshin Impact - Your saga continues on PS5 consoles

The gates of Purgatory have blown wide open, and Azazel's dark armies fester at its very heart. It's up to you to blast your way through his demonic hordes and face his grotesque children, the Nephilim. 

🤝 Champions Unite
Choose from four distinct Champions with unique perks and embark on a violent quest for redemption. Watch each other’s backs, and leave nothing standing.

🏰 Halls of the Damned
Fight your way across multiple levels spread across three brutal biomes. Many terrors await you, from countless swarming demons to towering Nephilim, each hellbent on your destruction. 

⚖ Judgement's Tools
Arm yourselves and choose from an arsenal of seven devastating weapons. Whether you're looking to spray, slice, pierce, or obliterate, our armory has you covered. 

🃏 Fury and Fortune
Upgrade your armaments with frightening elemental fury and equip Tarot cards to converge, power up, and maximize your team's abilities.

Celebrate the spooky season in Monster Hunter Wilds from Oct 22 - Nov 12 with the Festival of Accord: Dreamspell seasonal event! Visit the Grand Hub for a host of haunting decorations, trick or treat yourself to special food, forge fiendish new armor sets, and more!
-------
About Monster Hunter Wilds
Monster Hunter Wilds is the next generation of the acclaimed Monster Hunter series.

You are a monster hunter, protecting the balance of the ecosystem and hunting monsters in a world with dynamic, ever-changing environments. Use the resources you gain from hunts to craft ever more powerful weapons and armor in your quest to unravel the mysteries of the new lands.

Experience the most evolved action and improved immersion in the series in Monster Hunter Wilds, available now on PS5.
